name: show.*
description: This library exposes a show namespace that provides a number of higher level functions
useful for rendering tfjs concepts. They lean towards being opinionated rather than flexible
but are generally combinations of Renderers (see below), so one can easily roll their own.

subheadings.name: Model Inpsection
description: We have utility functions for common cases like Scalar, 1D,
2D, 3D and 4D tensors, as well a number of functions to initialize
tensors in ways useful for machine learning.

description: This section shows the main Tensor related classes in TensorFlow.js and
